-th%E1%BB%A9-h%E1%BB%93ng-k%E1%BB%B3-hi%E1%BA%BFn-ti%E1%BB%87p-thi-d%C4%A9-h%E1%BB%B7/poem-C_3HJr5EP3UBABlTFV4Nlw">Nguyên nhật thích tiếp Lạng - Bằng quân thứ hồng kỳ hiến tiệp thi dĩ hỷ - 元日適接諒平軍次紅旗獻捷詩以喜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94ng-Th%E1%BB%A5/Ti%E1%BB%87p-d%C6%B0-o%C3%A1n/poem-PlDg5eeVM3Xu6Frq0u5Fog">Tiệp dư oán - 婕妤怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94ng-Th%E1%BB%A5/author-G6Ov20BPmMttyfqss33i8w">Ông Thụ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Tr%C6%B0ng-N%E1%BB%AF-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-8atAKC4TsgLcqLn5xl4nZw">Vịnh Trưng Nữ Vương - 詠徵女王</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Huy-O%C3%A1nh/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-nZpuYY0I_gKn_a148N9zWA">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Huy-O%C3%A1nh/author-dr5ryihj5N63kZ-8HnRW6A">Nguyễn Huy Oánh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-giang-th%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-t4JtQEnkNj1C5SwsVUr3jg">Xuân nhật giang thôn kỳ 3 - 春日江村其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
